unidue.ub.statistics.media.monographs

Class Manifestation

  • java.lang.Object
    • unidue.ub.statistics.media.monographs.Manifestation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Manifestation
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable
    Representation of one manifestation characterized by given document number and a specific callNo (shelfmark). One Document can contain several Item objects and gives access to the Event objects connected to these items. It also holds the Bibliographic data in MAB-xml format
    Version:
    1
    Author:
    Frank Lützenkirchen, Eike Spielberg
